{"tid":377042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先有條杜拜佬問我借錢","createTime":"2017-08-27T12:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T18:26:08.000Z","uid":138587,"like":33,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95615f739753002347b2dcc156760960a2df9f22","tid":377042,"uid":138587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"頭先係地鐵站<br />\n有條友同我講佢係杜拜人<br />\n黎香港旅行比人偷曬d嘢 <br />\nshow埋張報失紙俾我睇<br />\n話屋企人聽日先黎香港<br />\n問我借200蚊 話屋企人翻到黎還翻俾我<br />\n咁我半信半疑俾左50蚊佢 話唔洗還<br />\n之後講完thank就走左<br />\n有無巴打試過<br />\n大家覺得我係咪俾人撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫到就幫啦 人地俾人偷曬d嘢好可憐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老西都唔俾啦 一定係呃錢"},{"pid":"41eaa990b161b33bff702ef9f1fbcd61d9a0d3c7","tid":377042,"uid":8678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"假"},{"pid":"d8de689644ad2d03ca7685af681a1c4960efafe0","tid":377042,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555a4f9381278c6b36b4b4223720886019856095","tid":377042,"uid":67010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:35:03.000Z","msg":"杜拜佬講咩話先"},{"pid":"7caeeafa1c8c71a16db00a312c9301aa93b43fcd","tid":377042,"uid":138587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>杜拜佬講咩話先</blockquote><br />\n講英文"},{"pid":"2a269f58180d602bdf9707a3e01309151dd6ca8f","tid":377042,"uid":33572,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"地鐵站可以去客務中心留個人資料借車飛<br />\n<br />\n報警可以求警協助 <br />\n<br />\n根本有心呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737dd711858b44aba7e27f73e87da44bf7b8adbb","tid":377042,"uid":33572,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"你點分得出南亞人同杜拜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都係咁既色"},{"pid":"62c5d2b9ff139cbc5a781a86a91b4d55e0d34625","tid":377042,"uid":3232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"樓主聽日會變富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4983f10dfbdbfd4ee450fcd7f53e3388845ed7","tid":377042,"uid":138587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵站可以去客務中心留個人資料借車飛<br />\n<br />\n報警可以求警協助 <br />\n<br />\n根本有心呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢用iphone 然後隻眼珠啡色<br />\n唔多似南亞人<br />\n同埋佢問我借錢食飯"},{"pid":"f6939a97c2224c93b013ef60e63ffebe0cf0b525","tid":377042,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"比左負皮<br />\n如果你真係信外地人唔見晒啲嘢想幫人就唔止比50$<br />\n所以你嗰$50我認為你純粹係打發人走 而唔係有心幫<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n攞張報失紙行騙好似以前已經有人講過"},{"pid":"30dd8582df8d7ceab06435bb0f1694649e143e95","tid":377042,"uid":15558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"你叫佢問你「當我一晚夜遊杜拜如何過」"},{"pid":"b39d4d5bcde1ed4ff062646b4f9fa30bf78e7663","tid":377042,"uid":138587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比左負皮<br />\n如果你真係信外地人唔見晒啲嘢想幫人就唔止比50$<br />\n所以你嗰$50我認為你純粹係打發人走 而唔係有心幫<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n攞張報失紙行騙好似以前已經有人講過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我學生 無咁多cash係身<br />\n廢事去按機 所以俾50蚊"},{"pid":"026c1c40c9de6fd90251dd64a691ed6fd76d7531","tid":377042,"uid":71343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先係地鐵站<br />\n有條友同我講佢係杜拜人<br />\n黎香港旅行比人偷曬d嘢 <br />\nshow埋張報失紙俾我睇<br />\n話屋企人聽日先黎香港<br />\n問我借200蚊 話屋企人翻到黎還翻俾我<br />\n咁我半信半疑俾左50蚊佢 話唔洗還<br />\n之後講完thank就走左<br />\n有無巴打試過<br />\n大家覺得我係咪俾人撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫到就幫啦 人地俾人偷曬d嘢好可憐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老西都唔俾啦 一定係呃錢</blockquote><br />\n上次係麻油地睇睇下錶拍我膊頭<br />\n同你一樣又show d野比我睇<br />\n又話自己香港出世但又話黎旅行係中環比人偷哂d野9唔撚搭8咁!<br />\n之後問我要錢坐車返中環我話比錢佢坐地鐵啦<br />\n佢又唔知點但就擺撚到明呃錢唔撚理佢啦"},{"pid":"0b17bdd73664430aea2fbcf0042f7355c0d8567a","tid":377042,"uid":138587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先係地鐵站<br />\n有條友同我講佢係杜拜人<br />\n黎香港旅行比人偷曬d嘢 <br />\nshow埋張報失紙俾我睇<br />\n話屋企人聽日先黎香港<br />\n問我借200蚊 話屋企人翻到黎還翻俾我<br />\n咁我半信半疑俾左50蚊佢 話唔洗還<br />\n之後講完thank就走左<br />\n有無巴打試過<br />\n大家覺得我係咪俾人撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫到就幫啦 人地俾人偷曬d嘢好可憐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老西都唔俾啦 一定係呃錢</blockquote><br />\n上次係麻油地睇睇下錶拍我膊頭<br />\n同你一樣又show d野比我睇<br />\n又話自己香港出世但又話黎旅行係中環比人偷哂d野9唔撚搭8咁!<br />\n之後問我要錢坐車返中環我話比錢佢坐地鐵啦<br />\n佢又唔知點但就擺撚到明呃錢唔撚理佢啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢咁可憐 好難拒絕"},{"pid":"dcf5e4f30489b3b6d73068cc907524144ef960b3","tid":377042,"uid":71343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>頭先係地鐵站<br />\n有條友同我講佢係杜拜人<br />\n黎香港旅行比人偷曬d嘢 <br />\nshow埋張報失紙俾我睇<br />\n話屋企人聽日先黎香港<br />\n問我借200蚊 話屋企人翻到黎還翻俾我<br />\n咁我半信半疑俾左50蚊佢 話唔洗還<br />\n之後講完thank就走左<br />\n有無巴打試過<br />\n大家覺得我係咪俾人撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫到就幫啦 人地俾人偷曬d嘢好可憐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老西都唔俾啦 一定係呃錢</blockquote><br />\n上次係麻油地睇睇下錶拍我膊頭<br />\n同你一樣又show d野比我睇<br />\n又話自己香港出世但又話黎旅行係中環比人偷哂d野9唔撚搭8咁!<br />\n之後問我要錢坐車返中環我話比錢佢坐地鐵啦<br />\n佢又唔知點但就擺撚到明呃錢唔撚理佢啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢咁可憐 好難拒絕</blockquote><br />\n係唔合理囉!你要錢搭車咪比20你坐囉<br />\n地鐵一定夠比啦!就算呃都呃20姐<br />\n但佢個撚樣仲唔知足咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個銀包比撚埋你好唔好呀!<br />\n最後一蚊都唔比佢!<br />\n之前有排夜晚返屋企好多大陸妹又話黎旅行比人偷野無錢食錢!"},{"pid":"d7071fbdb917c7ea66a12450aa46d8916f165c1f","tid":377042,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬會唔做埋杜拜富豪嘅恩人，跟住發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507a4cdff947aa3708e22fe667f16eceadac4ed4","tid":377042,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個覺得係班南亞蝗扮杜拜土豪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27e9c520d7e07a9ee341bfd217223966cae9600","tid":377042,"uid":101580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"係某西鐵站外遇過<br />\n一鳩樣係杜拜嚟 唔見曬嘢 有偷失紙 家人聽日先來到香港 問我借錢食飯 重帶住另一個中東人<br />\n俾條友呃咗十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fca73c14fffb3d785028cdbb7a413a84cbd6f7","tid":377042,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"018585b5defdc98f1a2369c9ec776cdd0da4bbe9","tid":377042,"uid":71343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪得我一個覺得係班南亞蝗扮杜拜土豪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南亞蝗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢埋黎同我講英文<br />\n我死都同佢講中文<br />\n之後佢就講中文"},{"pid":"c999a4c2f5f9fbd4e1f63c781de6b1c2b92d267d","tid":377042,"uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":